  "title": "Class LogEntry",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LogEntry' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LogEntry' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Core_LogEntry'>Class LogEntry    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Core/LogEntry.cs#L42'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Default implementation of ILogEntry containing all log data.\nImmutable after creation to ensure thread safety.\nAOT-compatible: No reflection, value-based semantics.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class LogEntry : ILogEntry</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LogEntry.html'>LogEntry</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.html'>ILogEntry</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.